8AQ">Phóng Hạc đình ký - 放鶴亭記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Tang-Trung-2/poem-xVo9muuF2eAhEr09snbNTQ">Tang Trung 2 - 桑中 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/Thanh-M%C3%B4n-ca-t%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%C3%A0i-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-8a4MwFyitvaVu2ZXBvzpQw">Thanh Môn ca tống đông đài Trương phán quan - 青門歌送東台張判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%E1%BB%A9c-vi-2/poem-XJSa6s6n6hImuqX2Fm-Llg">Thức vi 2 - 式微 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-gia-nhi/poem-_idfLH-CKR1qIP7JofaBPA">Xuân nhật thị gia nhi - 春日示家兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
